          </h1>

          <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">LP evaluating fund opportunities visits 12 PE firm websites. 9 have outdated team bios, vague investment thesis, no track record, difficult contact. One modern site with clear fund strategy, portfolio showcase, measurable IRR, easy LP inquiry. Which gets the meeting? For PE fundraising, clarity = competence = capital.</p>

